---
title: "US20 — Inactivity alerts"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>NotificationsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ManageNotificationPrefs / ScheduleReminder
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile (notification_prefs) · WorkoutSession
  A->>B: toggle "Inactivity alerts" on
  B->>C: setEnabled(inactivity_alert, true)
  C->>E: updateNotificationPrefs(userId, prefs)
  E-->>C: saved
  C->>E: scheduleReminder(inactivity_alert) - scan listEndedSessions vs commitment
  E-->>C: no ended session for N days → scheduled
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (prefs)
  B-->>A: "You have not worked out since..." (rule-based, not AI)
  note over E: prefs via ProfileGateway → profiles (RLS) [BUILT] -<br/>scheduleReminder via NotificationGateway over WorkoutGateway.listEndedSessions [planned] - rule-based, no AI
